a\boxplus b:=\min\{a,b\}
a\oplus b:=\max\{a,b\}
\Bbb R_\uparrow:=\Bbb R\cup\{\infty\}
\Bbb R_\downarrow:=\Bbb R\cup\{-\infty\}.
